al activity (such as theft, drug and alcohol crimes, property crimes) related to substance use. Engagement in delinquent-type behaviours (such as drinking and driving, aggression and fighting, bullying, carrying weapons to school, buying and selling drugs, gang involvement, truancy, suspension and expulsion, and disobeying rules in general) related to substance use. It was not expected that the included BIs would have adverse effects on the primary or secondary outcomes."}
